body:
Had a blast today from getting my Parts in the mail to the final construction to the satisfaction of everything working.

Specs: 
2x Dell E2414H 24-Inch Widescreen Monitors.
Corsair Obsidian Series 750D Full Tower Case
Intel Core i7-4790K Processor (4.0GH/z --> OC'd to 4.40GH/z)
GeForce GTX 770 Superclocked ACX Cooler 4 GB GDDR5 (1111MH/z)
MSI Z97-GD65 Motherboard
Kingston HyperX FURY 16GB Kit (2x8GB) 1866MHz 
Corsair Hydro Series Liquid CPU cooler
250GB Samsung Evo 840 SSD
1TB Western Digital HDD
Windows 7 Pro.

Total cost was about 2000$

Some pictures of the build.
